args.question: Prepare data to count the number of paintings depicting War for each year.

xmode.content:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

data = {'1536': 1, '1770': 1, '1799': 1}

# Extract years and counts
years = list(data.keys())
counts = list(data.values())

# Create a bar chart
plt.figure(figsize=(8, 6))
plt.bar(years, counts, color='skyblue')
plt.xlabel('Year')
plt.ylabel('Number of Paintings')
plt.title('Number of Paintings Depicting War by Year')
plt.xticks(rotation=45)
plt.tight_layout()

# Save the plot
plt.savefig('/home/ubuntu/workspace/XMODE-LLMCompiler/ceasura_langgraph/experiments/log//10/plot-out.png')
plt.close()
